title: Cheesy Bean & Veggie Enchiladas with Sour Cream & Tomato Salad
description: Enchiladas – what could be more fun? Take one part tasty beans and veg, one part soft tortillas, then combine them and top the whole
thing with melty cheesy goodness. With a fresh tomato salad, this is a sure-fire winner.

